This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, (1) To identify and evaluate all randomised controlled trials comparing nitrates and alternative interventions in acute heart failure in adults;, (2) To determine the effect of route of administration of nitrates on clinical outcome in acute heart failure in adults;, (3) To quantify the effect of different nitrate preparations on clinical outcome in acute heart failure in adults;, (4) To evaluate the safety and tolerability of nitrates in acute heart failure in adults